# Branch Policy

- All work MUST target the branch **v2-fastify-architecture**.

- If a task mentions any other branch, STOP and request architecture approval.

- Every response MUST end with a "GIT BLOCK" including commands to commit and push to **v2-fastify-architecture**.

- Respect AKIS guard-rails (architecture/stack/patterns/MCP). If a request violates them, STOP and ask for approval instead of proceeding.
